    "6. Identify and explain stages of Programming."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "It includes the stages of Analyze, Plan, Code, Test and Maintenance.\n",
    "Analyze: At these stages we need to identify the need of the customer or the actual problem to address.\n",
    "Plan: At this stage we identify the input required and the process under which the inputs should pass through to provide the expected output in logical order.\n",
    "Code: At this stage we prepare the script of the actual code to provide instruction for the computer to perform the required task.\n",
    "Test: Once we have the code, we need to check whether the code is free of bug or not and able to address the purpose meant for.\n",
    "Maintenance: At this stage we provide up date or fix some unforeseen issues which might be overlooked during coding.\n"
   ]
